## General Repository Rules

### Language Requirements

**IMPORTANT**: All content in this repository MUST be in English, including but not limited to:

- Source code (variable names, function names, class names, etc.)
- Code comments and docstrings
- Documentation files (README, CHANGELOG, etc.)
- Git commit messages and PR titles/descriptions
- Configuration files and scripts
- Test cases and test descriptions (except for deliberately multilingual test cases, if any)
- Error messages and log messages
- Any other text content in the repository
